description: This top 10% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 19, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 152, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, Nine Lives for South, and Stringalong for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
